      <title>纽约美铁列车服务在延误和取消后恢复</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-02/nyc-bound-nj-transit-amtrak-train-service-suspended-delayed</link>
      <description><![CDATA[经过周一早些时候的长时间延误和取消，进出纽约宾夕法尼亚车站的美国铁路公司列车服务现已恢复。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-02/nyc-bound-nj-transit-amtrak-train-service-suspended-delayed</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 02 Dec 2024 15:20:06 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
